---
title: Blackened Tilapia with Crispy Potatoes and Blistered Veggies
description: For a lighter preparation, we’re blackening this flaky fish with a potent mix of spices rather than batter frying. A side of crispy roasted potatoes and caramelized vegetables is the perfect accompaniment.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5703c5634dab718b4a8b4568.jpg
